com.mozium.api.script.assertion

Class MoziumAssert

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mozium.api.script.assertion.MoziumAssert

  • public class MoziumAssert
extends java.lang.Object
    Assertion tool class. Presents assertion methods more for testing some properties for the html component in page. The methods are always TestElement, [, extrat params] , expectedValue .
    Version:
    1.0.1
    Author:
    mba
